{"id":232921256,"title":"甜點#烤蘋果🍎","content":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/4e74a439-0191-4a2a-8268-55af2947c01d/1280.jpeg\n因為閃不喜歡吃水果，所以變著花樣讓他吃。\n這道烤蘋果作法超簡單，成品奶香四溢，果肉鬆軟，很適合當作飯後甜點或宵夜。\n🍎食譜/1人份🍎\n蘋果*1\n無鹽奶油適量\n二砂糖適量\n焦糖（optional, 細砂糖90g，水30g)\n糖粉適量\n🍎步驟🍎\n1. 烤箱預熱180ºC\n2. 蘋果切上蓋，挖空中柱。\n3. 奶油切小塊塞進空洞，再填滿二砂。\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1f26fe85-3e75-429c-a047-f68049a27d57/1280.jpeg\n4. 放進烤箱中層，烤40分鐘以上。\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/4294401a-4027-4568-aa78-4c012ab44171/1280.jpeg\n這次是用全聯特價6顆89元的小蘋果，大顆的可以烤到1小時。\n5. 出爐後表面可以淋焦糖，或是撒一點糖粉裝飾。簡單完成一道甜點～\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/fb4bafba-673e-4a86-92b5-ee9a12d30361/1280.jpeg\n配上黑咖啡或茶品，就是配影集的好夥伴👌","excerpt":"因為閃不喜歡吃水果，所以變著花樣讓他吃。這道烤蘋果作法超簡單，成品奶香四溢，果肉鬆軟，很適合當作飯後甜點或宵夜。食譜/1人份，蘋果*1，無鹽奶油適量，二砂糖適量，焦糖（optional， 細砂糖90g","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d7db42a8-bedb-4ea2-96a7-c9034f4dd89a","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-19T15:35:04.960Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-19T15:35:04.960Z","commentCount":11,"likeCount":135,"tags":[],"topics":["烹飪","食譜","在家輕鬆做","懶人料理","甜點"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"烹飪","forumAlias":"cooking","school":"AJ與四季","department":"a.wh09","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":134},{"id":"4b018f48-e184-445f-adf1-fc8e04ba09b9","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/4e74a439-0191-4a2a-8268-55af2947c01d/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/1f26fe85-3e75-429c-a047-f68049a27d57/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/4294401a-4027-4568-aa78-4c012ab44171/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/fb4bafba-673e-4a86-92b5-ee9a12d30361/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","medi